front.title: •IT-O (Eyetee-Oh)
front.gametext: When at Detention Block Corridor, adds X to your Force drains there, where X = the number of captives present. Immune to Restraining Bolt.
front.lore: Floating prisoner interrogation droid. Uses probes and needles to dispense truth drugs and perform 'surgery.' Sensors determine subject's pain threshold and truthfulness.

canceledBy: Force drain bonus is canceled by Captive Fury
